@startuml
title Coordinator And Worker Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 135
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam TitleFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #5E5A53
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #5E5A53
  LifeLineBorderColor #1D1D1D
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F2E9D9
  ParticipantBorderColor #1D1D1D
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #EFE6D8
  ParticipantFontColor #161616
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5EBDD
  BorderColor #8C2721
  FontColor #7B1E1E
}

actor User as user
participant Coordinator as coord
participant "Research Worker" as research
participant "Implementation Worker" as impl
participant "Runtime / Hooks /\nTask System" as runtime

user -> coord : 提出目标
coord -> runtime : Spawn research workers
runtime -> research : isolated context
research --> runtime : findings
runtime --> coord : research result
coord -> coord : synthesize findings
coord -> runtime : Spawn implementation worker
runtime -> impl : isolated subagent
impl --> runtime : code changes + self-check
runtime --> coord : implementation result
coord --> user : 综合结论 / 风险 / 下一步

note right of coord
Coordinator 负责综合与分发，
不只是转发 worker 产出。
end note

@enduml
